VALUES (19,'CMFK','Cycling from Mount Fuji to Kyoto','NULL','Rather than zipping straight to Kyoto from Tokyo in a matter of hours on the shinkansen high-speed train, intrepid travelers can saddle up and take the slow road on this 12-day trip. Following an e-bike tour of Tokyo, things take a more strenuous turn on a ride around Fuji Five Lakes, with Japan''s most iconic mountain as a backdrop.The route also takes in traditional villages near Lake Biwa, before ending in the ancient capital of Kyoto, with its abundance of peaceful temples and traditional ryokan, or inns.',NULL,NULL,9,NULL,21,0,0,1,0,0,0,0,1,0,1,600,4200,19,'https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/best-adventure-vacations-2018/index.html');
