VALUES (22,'IRMBLB','The Ice Run: Motor biking across frozen Lake Baikal','NULL','With a Russian motorbike and sidecar for transport, the Ice Run is a dream trip for adventure fiends. Starting and finishing in Irkutsk, this challenging ride follows remote forest tracks and long routes over the snowy, open steppe, before taking to the icy expanse of Lake Baikal, the deepest lake in the world. 4x4 support vehicles are on hand, as is GPS to help find essential stops for food and fuel. There are classes on ice riding and motorcycle maintenance before the trip sets out.',NULL,NULL,7,NULL,11,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1,0,1,1599,7999,22,'https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/best-adventure-vacations-2018/index.html');
