VALUES (25,'RTN','Rhino trekking in Namibia','NULL','Setting off before sunrise in 4x4s from Namibia''s remote Desert Rhino Camp, this trek takes searching for endangered rhinos to another level. With experts from Save The Rhinos, travelers can join trackers on foot to get up close to these majestic creatures once they''ve been located. ',NULL,NULL,4,NULL,14,0,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,1,2500,9000,25,'https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/best-adventure-vacations-2018/index.html');
