VALUES (26,'HECR','Heli-exploring the Canadian Rockies','NULL','A week-long adventure in the Canadian Rockies is likely to be many outdoor types'' idea of a dream vacation. Throw in a private helicopter to allow access to some of the range''s most remote passes, meadows and peaks and it''s hard to imagine a better break. After two days spent acclimatizing in Banff National Park, the chopper takes travelers into the high country of the Purcell Mountains for a 72-hour adventure, with experts leading hikes across snow fields and valleys.',NULL,NULL,2,NULL,23,0,0,1,1,0,0,0,1,0,1,2500,5000,26,'https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/best-adventure-vacations-2018/index.html');
